<MainLayout title="Agder's Best Gamer">
  <Tournament>
    <h1 class="title">Agders Best Gamer</h1>
    <img
      src="/betalan/tournaments/ABGRandomGamesImage.png"
      alt="Prizes for ABG 2025"
      class="responsive-img"
    />
    <h2 class="section-title">What is Agder's Best Gamer?</h2>

    <p class="paragraph">
      Agder's Best Gamer is a yearly competition organised by BETALan to determine the best gamer in Agder. 
      Players compete in a wide variety of games, spanning survival, rhythm, puzzle solving and more. No matter
      what games you play, you have a chnace of winning and cliaming the gamer crown of Agder for yourself.
    </p>
    <p class="paragraph">
    If you think you got what it takes, then sign up and show us what you got!
    </p>

    <h2 class="section-title">Prizes</h2>

    <img
      src="/betalan/tournaments/ABG2025Premier.png"
      alt="Prizes for ABG 2025"
      class="responsive-img"
    />

    <ul class="link-center">
      <li class="list-item">
